{"tid":1069974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【印度商排華】焚燒中國貨 要求對華徵最高500%進口關稅","createTime":"2019-03-20T10:21:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T12:12:25.000Z","uid":47359,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0fbbdd7b4312e3b6994040e2d181979f301601d1","tid":1069974,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T10:21:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190320/59390265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190320%2F59390265&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9EzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=6097bb0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190320%2F59390265&h=02e2d376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190320/59390265</a><br />\n<br />\n路透社周二（19日）報道，印度市民在全國逾1,500個地方示威抵制中國貨，有數百名新德里商人，焚燒中國貨物，要求當局提高對中國商品的進口關稅，以減少便宜中國貨對印度製造商的傷害。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，中國在印巴衝突上，支持巴基斯坦，又阻止聯合國將親巴的武裝組織穆罕默德軍首領阿茲哈（Maulana Masood Azhar）列作恐怖分子，惹惱印度人。發動示威的全印度貿易商聯合會（CAIT）建議印度當局，對中國進口商品徵收300%至500%關稅。<br />\n<br />\nCAIT稱，大部分中國進口商品，包括玩具、電子產品、手機、電器、日用品等商品，以便宜價格掠奪當地市場。CAIT亦指，印度中小企業有能力生產這些產品，品質亦比中國貨佳，且價格合理，敦促政府支持當地中小企。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"c015a63dcda494e41807f9d4c3d769f807c9fdc3","tid":1069974,"uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T10:22:24.000Z","msg":"中國又嬴"},{"pid":"cffb086337b2f860ae778513eba2ca5f40b9732a","tid":1069974,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T10:26:45.000Z","msg":"印巴衝突 印度證實核潛艦曾待命作戰 前印度駐巴大使：我哋關注中國 唔係巴基斯坦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1069318\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1069318</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0ab7353edf8dea1c019b609339e096f51d1fa8b0","tid":1069974,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T12:12:25.000Z","msg":"屌你老母蚑共根本同蛔狗有檯底交易"}]}